release.name: Fess 14.11.0
release.body:
The CodeLibs Project is pleased to announce that Fess 14.11 release is now available.
Fess is a very powerful and easily deployable Enterprise Full Text Search Server, 
and you can install and run it quickly on any platform with a Java runtime environment.
This release supports OpenSearch 2.11 as a search engine and
provides Web Crawling, Shared Folder Crawling, and DB Crawling features.
All feedback and contributions are welcome.
Please create [a new topic](https://discuss.codelibs.org/c/fessen/) in case of a problem or question
and also, code contributions are welcome via pull requests.

issue.title: Update Log Message and Refactor PathMapping
issue.body: The log message content in the `PathMapping` class has been updated for better clarity and readability. Additionally, the variable `pathMapper` has been renamed to `pathMapperFunc` to reflect its functionality more accurately.

commits.message: fix #2774 Refactor variable name and update log message

issue.title: WebCrawler returns no results
issue.body:
Dear FESS-developers/-users,

I have just started using version 14.10 and cannot get any results from the web crawler. Please see my crawler configuration below.

![fess_crawler_config](https://github.com/codelibs/fess/assets/29715624/89108651-319a-4623-9668-bb5a8df44d3e)

Under System Infos > Crawling Infos > Session-ID there are no results listed. fess-crawler.log does not offer any further hints. 

`{"@timestamp":"2023-10-13T10:33:41.588Z","log.level": "INFO","message":"Target URL: https://press.un.org/en/content/press-release", "ecs.version": "1.2.0","service.name":"fess","event.dataset":"crawler","process.thread.name":"WebFsCrawler","log.logger":"org.codelibs.fess.helper.WebFsIndexHelper"}

{"@timestamp":"2023-10-13T10:33:41.589Z","log.level": "INFO","message":"Included URL: https://press\\.un\\.org/en/2023/\\w+\\.doc\\.htm", "ecs.version": "1.2.0","service.name":"fess","event.dataset":"crawler","process.thread.name":"WebFsCrawler","log.logger":"org.codelibs.fess.helper.WebFsIndexHelper"}

{"@timestamp":"2023-10-13T10:33:41.590Z","log.level": "INFO","message":"Excluded URL: (?i).*(css|js|jpeg|jpg|gif|png|bmp|wmv|xml|ico|exe)", "ecs.version": "1.2.0","service.name":"fess","event.dataset":"crawler","process.thread.name":"WebFsCrawler","log.logger":"org.codelibs.fess.helper.WebFsIndexHelper"}
`
I carefully read through the documentation and some other related issues, but that did not help. Do have any ideas about what is going wrong? Any help would be appreciated. 

Thank you in advance

Andrei
